Topics
    Media queries (Responsive web design) 
    our website/app should be Responsive on all the devices (mobiles, laptops, desktop, projectors)

Basic syntax

    @media (condition) {
        CSS rules 
    }

list of devices - all, screens, print

we can have conditions like, 
    width,min-width, max-width - viewport width
    height, min-height, max-height - viewport height

conditional cases - AND OR NOT (and , not)

add media queries at the last, media queries will not have any specificity

Assignment - Try to research on the specificity when using media queries

List of devices width
    320px - small phones
    480px - large phones
    780px - tablets
    1024px - laptops
    1200px - Desktops